        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P14074">https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P14074</a></p>
<p>这道题目，暴力只能拿到40分。</p>
<p>但是仔细观察114514年就可以发现，4个二进制数为一个周期循环，奇数1和偶数1的个数一致。</p>
<p>比如0-3 二进制是：0 1 10 11，偶数个一的数有：<code>0</code> <code>11</code>，奇数：<code>1</code> <code>10</code>，奇数个一的和就是<code>0+3=3</code>，偶数为<code>1+2=3</code>，3=3.</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://quanac-lcx.github.io/post-images/1761481213058.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>然后可以发现公式：</p>
<p class='katex-block'><span class="katex-display"><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">总</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">和</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">区</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">间</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">个</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">数</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>∗</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">区</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">间</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">个</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">数</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">总和=区间个数^2*4-区间个数
</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.36687em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">总</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">和</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8641079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">区</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">间</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">个</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord cjk_fallback">数</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8641079999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">∗</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">4</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">−</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">区</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">间</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">个</span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">数</span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p>然后写代码：</p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">#include&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;
using namespace std;
typedef unsigned long long ll;

ll arr[]={0,1,3,3,7,7,7,14,22};

bool check(int n){
	int sum1=0;
	//转化为二进制
	string a=bitset&lt;64&gt;(n).to_string();
	for(int i=0;i&lt;a.size();i++){
		if(a[i]=='1')
			sum1++;
	}
	return sum1%2==1;
}
ll f(ll n){
	if(n&lt;=8) return arr[n]; //防止减出负数
	ll shuLiang=(n-4)/4;
	ll ans=shuLiang*shuLiang*4-shuLiang;
	for(int i=shuLiang*4;i&lt;=n;i++){
		check(i)?ans+=i:0;
	}
	return ans;
}
int main(){
	ll l,r,ans=0;
	cin&gt;&gt;l&gt;&gt;r;
	cout&lt;&lt;f(r)-f(l-1);
	return 0;
}

</code></pre>
